Title: Jalsa
Writer: Vedula Ravi Kiran (script coordinator), Saigopal (script coordinator), Trivikram Srinivas (dialogue), Trivikram Srinivas (screenplay), Trivikram Srinivas (story)
Actors: Pawan Kalyan, Ileana D'Cruz, Mukesh Rishi, Kamalinee Mukherjee
Plot: Sanjay Sahu (Pawan Kalyan) is a happy-go-lucky type youth. Bhagyamati (Ileana) falls in love with him and Sanjay accepts her proposal after waiting for a while.
